18 SERVICES PROVIDERS RESULTING FROM THE ANNUAL RATE INCREASES REQUIRED
19 BY THIS SECTION.
20 SECTION 3. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect July
21 1, 2026. Section 1 2 of this Act shall remain effective for a period of 2 years and, at the end
22 of June 30, 2028, Section 1 2 of this Act, with no further action required by the General
23 Assembly, shall be abrogated and of no further force and effect.
